rick Roberts|Andrew Thomas}}\n| extra11         = {{hlist|Boi-1da|[[Supa Dups]]{{ref|a|[a]}}|Ritter{{ref|a|[a]}}|{{nowrap|[[Di Genius]]}}{{ref|b|[b]}}}}\n| length11        = 4:05\n\n| title12         = [[One Dance]]\n| note12         = featuring [[Wizkid (musician)|Wizkid]] and [[Kyla (British singer)|Kyla]]\n| writer12        = {{hlist|Graham|Jefferies|Shebib|[[Wizkid (musician)|Ayodeji Balogun]]|Errol Reid|[[Kyla (British singer)|Kyla Smith]]}}\n| extra12         = {{hlist|Nineteen85|40{{ref|a|[a]}}|[[Wizkid (musician)|Wizkid]]{{ref|a|[a]}}|[[DJ Maphorisa]]{{ref|c|[c]}}}}\n| length12        = 2:54\n\n| title13         = Grammys\n| note13         = featuring [[Future (rapper)|Future]]\n| writer13        = {{hlist|Graham|Shebib|Wilburn|[[Southside (record producer)|Joshua Luellen]]|[[Cardo (record producer)|Ronald LaTour]]|Daveon Jackson}}\n| extra13         = {{hlist|40|[[Southside (record producer)|Southside]]|[[Cardo (record producer)|Cardo]]{{ref|a|[a]}}|Yung Exclusive{{ref|a|[a]}}}}\n| length13        = 3:40\n\n| title14         = Childs Play\n| writer14        = {{hlist|Graham|Shebib|[[Metro Boomin|Leland Wayne]]|Mark Morales|Darren Robinson|Damon Wimbley}}\n| extra14         = {{hlist|40|[[Metro Boomin]]{{ref|b|[b]}}|Ullman{{ref|b|[b]}}|Nineteen85{{ref|b|[b]}}}}\n| length14        = 4:01\n\n| title15         = [[Pop Style]] \n| writer15        = {{hlist|Graham|Samuels|Shebib|West|[[Sevn Thomas|Rupert Thomas, Jr.]]|[[Frank Dukes|Adam Feeney]]|[[Jay-Z|Shawn Carter]]}}\n| extra15         = {{hlist|[[Sevn Thomas]]|[[Frank Dukes]]|Boi-1da{{ref|b|[b]}}|40{{ref|b|[b]}}}}\n| length15        = 3:32\n\n| title16         = [[Too Good]]\n| note16          = featuring [[Rihanna]]\n| writer16        = {{hlist|Graham|Jefferies|Bidaye|Chin-Quee|[[Rihanna|Robyn Fenty]]|Andrew Hershey|[[Popcaan|Andre Sutherland]]|Atom Martin<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.swedishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Drake+feat.+Rihanna&titel=Too+Good&cat=s |title=Drake feat. Rihanna \u2013 Too Good