hi]] \u2013 co-production {{small|(3)}}\n* [[Frank Dukes]] \u2013 production {{small|(15)}}\n* [[Supa Dups]] \u2013 co-production {{small|(11)}}, additional production {{small|(16)}}\n* Yung Exclusive \u2013 co-production {{small|(13)}}\n* [[Di Genius]] \u2013 additional production {{small|(11)}}\n* Hagler \u2013 additional production {{small|(18)}}\n* Jordan Lewis \u2013 additional production {{small|(18)}}\n* [[Brian Alexander Morgan|Brian Morgan]] \u2013 co-production {{small|(2)}}\n* [[Nineteen85]] \u2013 production {{small|(5, 12, 16, 20)}}, co-production {{small|(9)}}, additional production {{small|(8, 14)}}\n* [[OZ (record producer)|OZ]] \u2013 additional production {{small|(3)}}\n* [[Ricci Riera]] \u2013 co-production {{small|(3)}}\n* [[Allen Ritter]] \u2013 co-production {{small|(11)}}\n* [[Southside (record producer)|Southside]] \u2013 production {{small|(13)}}\n* [[Stwo]] \u2013 co-production {{small|(6)}}\n* [[Majid Jordan|Jordan Ullman]] \u2013 production {{small|(4)}}, additional production {{small|(14)}}\n* [[Vinylz]] \u2013 additional production {{small|(3)}}\n* [[Kanye West]] \u2013 production {{small|(3)}}, additional production {{small|(4)}}\n* [[Wizkid (musician)|Wizkid]] \u2013 co-production {{small|(12)}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2016)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{albumchart|Australia|1|artist=Drake|album=Views|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 7, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Austria|20|artist=Drake|album=Views|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 19, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|3|artist=Drake|album=Views|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 6, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|13|artist=Drake|album=Views|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 6, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|BillboardCanada|1|artist=Drake|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 10, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Czech|19|artist=Drake|album=Views|row